class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Infrastructure\\Storage\\InMemoryRunAccessStore"
type: final class
summary: InMemoryRunAccessStore provides an in-memory implementation for persisting and retrieving RunAccessScope entities keyed by run ID. It serves as a transient storage layer for run access metadata within the agent core infrastructure.
